OL,3,CDoctors held 'outdated' views about
OL,4,CME, inquest into sufferer's death hears
OL,6,FIn June, she wrote a heartfelt note to
OL,7,Fher GP begging for help with feeding -
OL,8,Fsaying she was hungry but was unable
OL,9,Fto eat.
OL,11,F"I have been unable to sit up or chew
OL,12,Fsince March and the only person
OL,13,Fhelping me eat is my mum. I cannot get
OL,14,Fenough calories from a syringe," she
OL,15,Fwrote.
OL,17,F"Please help me get enough food to
OL,18,Flive."
