OL,3,CDoctors held 'outdated' views about
OL,4,CME, inquest into sufferer's death hears
OL,6,F"This can lead to completely
OL,7,Finappropriate management of someone
OL,8,Fgenuinely severely affected by a
OL,9,Fcondition with demonstrable organic
OL,10,Fpathology.
OL,12,F"A further point I wish to make is
OL,13,Fthat it would appear a considerable
OL,14,Fproportion of the staff at the RD&E,
OL,15,Fincluding some consultants, still hold
OL,16,Fan outdated understanding that ME/CFS
OL,17,F(chronic fatigue syndrome) has
OL,18,Fpsychological causes.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
