OL,3,CDoctors held 'outdated' views about
OL,4,CME, inquest into sufferer's death hears
OL,6,F"It is also apparent from the way
OL,7,FMaeve was treated during her last
OL,8,Fadmission that her illness was
OL,9,Fregarded by some of the hospital staff
OL,10,Fas her fault and her immobility was
OL,11,Fself-inflicted.
OL,13,F"Not unreasonably she is reluctant to
OL,14,Fbe readmitted to the hospital despite
OL,15,Fher precarious physical state.
OL,17,F"At the same time, you will need to
OL,18,Ftackle head on the dogma concerning
OL,19,Fthe cause of ME/CFS that some
OL,20,Fcolleagues are still perversely
OL,21,Fadhering to."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUyD@AOU}D@MO]
