OL,3,CDoctors held 'outdated' views about
OL,4,CME, inquest into sufferer's death hears
OL,6,FDr Weir also urged the hospital to
OL,7,Freadmit Miss Boothby-O'Neill for total
OL,8,Fparenteral nutrition feeding.
OL,10,F"I understand now from speaking to her
OL,11,Ffather that her nutritional status
OL,12,Fcontinues to be seriously compromised
OL,13,F` a situation which is potentially
OL,14,Flife-threatening," he wrote.
OL,16,F"I have experience of similar cases
OL,17,Fleading to death and Maeve's current
OL,18,Fclinical status shows all the initial
OL,19,Fhallmarks of this.
OL,26,@rD@AOUvD@RO]xD@AOU
