OL,3,CDoctors held 'outdated' views about
OL,4,CME, inquest into sufferer's death hears
OL,6,FThe inquest heard Dr Weir had first
OL,7,Fmet her in March 2021 by which time
OL,8,Fshe was confined to bed and had
OL,9,Fdifficulty eating and drinking.
OL,11,FHe said in the absence of a "magic
OL,12,Fbullet" treatment for ME, she faced a
OL,13,F"long struggle" to recover as
OL,14,Feffective treatments were several
OL,15,Fyears away from development.
