OL,3,CDoctors held 'outdated' views about
OL,4,CME, inquest into sufferer's death hears
OL,6,F"My only comment to that is there are
OL,7,Fnone so blind as cannot see.
OL,9,F"There are still plenty of medical
OL,10,Fprofessionals out there in the
OL,11,Fcommunity who are still inherent to
OL,12,Fthe dogma and sadly has a very
OL,13,Fseriously damaging effect on
OL,14,Funderstanding the true scientific
OL,15,Fnature of this condition."
OL,17,FThe inquest, which is scheduled to
OL,18,Flast two weeks, continues.
